{
  "id": "69ad3610f00981858affaa89",
  "title": "朝鮮語を漢字ローマ字混じりにする",
  "created": 1772959260,
  "updated": 1778197513,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ad3610f00981858affaa89",
      "text": "朝鮮語を漢字ローマ字混じりにする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959260,
      "updated": 1772959260
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad361c000000000039e2fc",
      "text": "韓国語を漢字ローマ字混じりにする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959260,
      "updated": 1772959321
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3659000000000039e2ff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959321,
      "updated": 1772959321
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad378e000000000039e313",
      "text": "#怪文書の書き方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959630,
      "updated": 1772959636
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad378e000000000039e314",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959630,
      "updated": 1772959630
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad4755000000000039e7b3",
      "text": "コンセプト：",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772963670,
      "updated": 1772963749
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad47a5000000000039e7b7",
      "text": "「日本語じゃないのに、なんかちょっと読める！」という不思議な体験をしてみよう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772963749,
      "updated": 1772963749
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad479f000000000039e7b6",
      "text": " このためになるべく量が多くて整った文章を変換した。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772963744,
      "updated": 1772963771
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad4755000000000039e7b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772963670,
      "updated": 1772963670
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad36b7000000000039e306",
      "text": "韓国語の中で漢字が存在する発音は漢字に変換する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959415,
      "updated": 1772959437
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3683000000000039e304",
      "text": " https://translatormind.com/translator-tool/hangul-to-hanja-translator/",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959363,
      "updated": 1772959414
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad36d1000000000039e308",
      "text": " これだけで結構読めるようになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959442,
      "updated": 1772959449
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad36cd000000000039e307",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959438,
      "updated": 1772959438
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad366f000000000039e302",
      "text": "ハングルをローマ字に変換する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959344,
      "updated": 1772959438
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3675000000000039e303",
      "text": " https://www.lexilogos.com/keyboard/korean_conversion.htm",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959350,
      "updated": 1772959411
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad366e000000000039e301",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959342,
      "updated": 1772959342
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad397a000000000039e74e",
      "text": "このままでは一音節当たりの文字数が多い（ddong💩みたいなものができてしまう）ので、IPA を利用して文字数を減らす",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772960123,
      "updated": 1772960220
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3a47000000000039e754",
      "text": "\ttable:置換",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772960328,
      "updated": 1772960334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad39dc000000000039e74f",
      "text": "\t\tkk → ḱ\ttt → t́\tpp → ṕ\tss → ś\tjj → ćh",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772960221,
      "updated": 1772960349
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3a5d000000000039e755",
      "text": "\t\teo → ɔ\teu → ɯ\tae → ɛ\toe → ø\tui → ɰi",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772960350,
      "updated": 1772960646
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3977000000000039e74d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772960120,
      "updated": 1772960120
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3ba0000000000039e772",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772960673,
      "updated": 1772960673
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3626000000000039e2fd",
      "text": "[https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/위키백과:알찬_글 秀逸な記事 (韓国語版ウィキベディア)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959270,
      "updated": 1772959551
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3741000000000039e30a",
      "text": " これの中に「日本（[https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/일본 일본]）」がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959553,
      "updated": 1772959581
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad375e000000000039e30d",
      "text": " \tお前ら、なんだかんだ日本大好きやんw[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959583,
      "updated": 1772959608
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3751000000000039e30c",
      "text": "\t量も内容も充実しているので取り敢えずこれでためそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959569,
      "updated": 1772959626
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3779000000000039e30e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959609,
      "updated": 1772959609
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd23290000000000f31c92",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778197289,
      "updated": 1778197289
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3779000000000039e30f",
      "text": "試した結果",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772959609,
      "updated": 1778197287
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd24070000000000baac3a",
      "text": " 自由研究的なであり、個人のプロジェクトに帰属すべきだと思ったので切り出し。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778197512,
      "updated": 1778197513
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd23090000000000f31c8e",
      "text": "\t✂ [/Summer498/朝鮮語を漢字ローマ字混じりにする]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
